### Register passenger
POST http://localhost:5000/api/public/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "fullName": "Alice Example",
  "homeAddress": "Main Street 1"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/public/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Price estimate
POST http://localhost:5000/api/public/price
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "distanceKm": 12.5,
  "durationMinutes": 18,
  "vehicleType": "Standard",
  "startTime": "2025-02-16T14:00:00Z",
  "loyaltyPoints": 230,
  "discountCode": "SUMMER24"
}

### Create ride (use passengerId from register response)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/public/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passengerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "pickupLat": 51.0,
  "pickupLng": 3.0,
  "dropoffLat": 51.01,
  "dropoffLng": 3.01,
  "pickupAddress": "Start",
  "dropoffAddress": "End"
}

### Send telemetry (vehicle simulator)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/telemetry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "timestamp": "2025-02-16T14:00:00Z",
  "latitude": 51.0,
  "longitude": 3.0,
  "speedKmh": 42.5,
  "batteryPercent": 78,
  "internalTempC": 40.2
}
